msgid "Packet steering settings were applied."
msgstr "接收数据包分流设置已应用。"

msgid "Stock CPU settings were applied."
msgstr "原厂 CPU 设置已应用。"

msgid "Confirm experimental overclock"
msgstr "确认实验性超频"

msgid "Overclocking loads the opt-in PLL driver and changes the AN7581 CPU frequency without changing voltage. It may cause overheating, data loss or an unreachable device. The firmware will monitor temperature, but this cannot remove all risk."
msgstr "超频会按需加载 PLL 驱动，并在不改变电压的情况下修改 AN7581 CPU 频率，可能造成过热、数据丢失或设备失联。固件会监测温度，但无法消除全部风险。"

msgid "Type OVERCLOCK to apply %d MHz and save it for future boots."
msgstr "输入 OVERCLOCK 以应用 %d MHz，并保存为后续启动策略。"

msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgid "The confirmation text does not match."
msgstr "确认文字不匹配。"

msgid "The experimental CPU frequency was applied."
msgstr "实验性 CPU 频率已应用。"

msgid "Apply overclock"
msgstr "应用超频"

msgid "The CPU was restored to the stock 1200 MHz policy."
msgstr "CPU 已恢复为原厂 1200 MHz 策略。"

msgid "Full-core RPS can distribute different receive flows across all four CPU cores. It does not turn the 2.5G port into a hardware-switched port and does not accelerate a single flow across multiple cores."
msgstr "全核 RPS 可以把不同接收数据流分配到四个 CPU 核心，但不会把 2.5G 口变成硬件交换端口，也不会让单条数据流跨多个核心加速。"

msgid "At the stock 1200 MHz policy, the experimental PLL driver remains unloaded and no CPU clock registers are accessed."
msgstr "在原厂 1200 MHz 策略下，实验性 PLL 驱动保持未加载，也不会访问 CPU 时钟寄存器。"

msgid "Apply RPS mode"
msgstr "应用 RPS 模式"

msgid "CPU frequency"
msgstr "CPU 频率"

msgid "Apply CPU policy"
msgstr "应用 CPU 策略"

msgid "Restore stock 1200 MHz"
msgstr "恢复原厂 1200 MHz"
